cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.IR 

This paper is about improving object detection using contextual information learned from human expectations. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep neural networks, which suggests it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the study involves human subjects and their expectations, which could place it in the categories of cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
